name: Portfolio
body:
I'm really exited about the idea of joining the programmers world , this past week has been great so far, lots of information and tons of stuff to learn, during the middle of the week I did struggle finding some of the information to resolve one of the home work assignments, but I did not back down until finally came to resolve the  assignment, left me with a pretty good feeling of accomplishment.
Starting a new industry field can be intimidating, but I Know I have made the right choice.
These two weeks we have been working on our personal portfolios, learning the ways of using HTML along with CSS, styling the page was fun.

Noe.
